Uthe uma kubulawa iphoyisa elilodwa kumele lokho kuthathwe njengokuthi kuvukelwa isizwe sonke. “Kumele bafakwe ekhulukuthu elimnyama impilo yabo yonke labo abenza lokhu. Kumele isigebengu sikusabe noma sicabangisise kahle ngaphambi kokwenza lokhu.” UCele ubekhuluma izolo ezindlini zombuso ePitoli kukhunjulwa amaphoyisa angu-28 ne-reserve elilodwa abulawa onyakeni wezimali ka-2017/2018. Uthe uhulumeni kumele ushaye umthetho wokuthi kufane nokuvikela uMbuso ukubulala noma ubekwe amacala amabili. Uthe kuzoshintshwa indlela okuqeqeshwa ngayo amaphoyisa nalabo abangena embuthweni. “Kumele uma isigebengu sicabanga ukuhlasela iphoyisa, sazi ukuthi akulona iphoyisa elizodindiliza kodwa yisona.” Uzwakalise ukukhathazeka ngokubulawa kwamaphoyisa wathi selokhu angena ngoFebhuwari njalo ngempalasonto ungcwaba amaphoyisa. Uthe uyalelwe ukuthi benze okuthile ukuqeda isihlava sokubulawa kwamaphoyisa. Ubalule ukuthi iphoyisa elidala alingcwabile lina-39 weminyaka elincane lina-22.